 provide an overall assessment of an individual\'s adaptability and flexibility across all areas. A higher total score indicates a greater overall adaptability and flexibility.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35'),(34,12,37,60,'High adaptability and flexibility','Higher scores in this subscale indicate a greater willingness to embrace change, try new experiences, and adapt to novel situations. Individuals with high scores in this area are likely to be open to new ideas and opportunities. The total score can provide an overall assessment of an individual\'s adaptability and flexibility across all areas. A higher total score indicates a greater overall adaptability and flexibility.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35'),(35,13,0,20,'No or little Problem Solving Skills','A higher score in this subscale indicates a strong ability to analyse and break down complex problems, identify root causes, and evaluate alternatives. Lower scores may suggest a need to enhance analytical problem-solving skills. Total Problem Solving & Creativity Score Thresholds Score <40 No or little Problem Solving Skills / Score 41-120 Medium Problem Solving Skills / Score 121-160 High Problem Solving Skills / Score 161-200 Excellent Problem Solving Skills.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35'),(36,13,21,60,'Medium Problem Solving Skills','A higher score in this subscale indicates a strong ability to analyse and break down complex problems, identify root causes, and evaluate alternatives. Lower scores may suggest a need to enhance analytical problem-solving skills. Total Problem Solving & Creativity Score Thresholds Score <40 No or little Problem Solving Skills / Score 41-120 Medium Problem Solving Skills / Score 121-160 High Problem Solving Skills / Score 161-200 Excellent Problem Solving Skills.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35'),(37,13,61,80,'High Problem Solving Skills','A higher score in this subscale indicates a strong ability to analyse and break down complex problems, identify root causes, and evaluate alternatives. Lower scores may suggest a need to enhance analytical problem-solving skills. Total Problem Solving & Creativity Score Thresholds Score <40 No or little Problem Solving Skills / Score 41-120 Medium Problem Solving Skills / Score 121-160 High Problem Solving Skills / Score 161-200 Excellent Problem Solving Skills.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35'),(38,13,81,100,'Excellent Problem Solving Skills','A higher score in this subscale indicates a strong ability to analyse and break down complex problems, identify root causes, and evaluate alternatives. Lower scores may suggest a need to enhance analytical problem-solving skills. Total Problem Solving & Creativity Score Thresholds Score <40 No or little Problem Solving Skills / Score 41-120 Medium Problem Solving Skills / Score 121-160 High Problem Solving Skills / Score 161-200 Excellent Problem Solving Skills.','2025-03-14 21:35:35','2025-03-14 21:35:35');
